st restaurant together the strawberry patch and they have been delighting restaurantgoers ever since the pappas brothers now own and operate nearly  restaurants in seven states their nine brands offer something for everyone from fresh gulf coast seafood to cajuninspired cuisine awardwinning steaks and the best texmex on planet texas in addition to being restaurant pioneers the pappas brothers are quite involved in their local community chris and harris give generously of their time to the boy scouts of america memorial hermann healthcare system the boys and girls club and many more community associations in short the pappas brothers are just your everyday exceptional entrepreneurs of greek descent who have made quite a name for themselves in the restaurant business or as harris likes to say the people business basically theyre just glad you like their food yes you and as long as you keep liking it theyll keep making it the pappas brothers opened their first restaurant in  and set out to serve only the highest quality food fulfill their guests every request and make sure everyone who walked in the door felt like family since then weve opened more than  restaurants and have become a leader in the hospitality industry but at pappas its still all about great food impeccable service and the people who make it happen from the truck driver who delivers only the freshest meats and seafood to the hostess greeting guests with a smile to the server setting down a custommade entrée with care everyone at pappas plays a role in our success were a family owned and operated company which means our core values have been passed down from generation to generation were constantly focused on innovation attention to detail and quality in everything we do over the years our steadfast values and topnotch team have kept prospective employees seeking us out and satisfied guests coming back pappas spirit the spirit of the pappas restaurants is embodied in our mission statement its what makes our company unique attracts new employees and guests and motivates our regulars to return again and again our goal to be a superior restaurant company through constant innovation attention to detail and a focus on quality in all we do our guests we are dedicated to greeting each person who walks through our doors with warmth and friendliness we create an outstanding dining experience through identifying and fulfilling guest expectations our team we believe that the greatest strength of pappas restaurants lies within our people we are committed to providing an exciting environment that recognizes initiative and performance we offer opportunities for growth and challenge individuals to achieve their best our communities we build relationships through participation and service and work together to help meet the needs of the community whats pappas up to in your community want to work with pappas our family is bigger than you think one of the things that makes pappas restaurants different is that we do more than simply run and operate our restaurants we own and drive the trucks that deliver the freshest meats and seafood we employ the electricians who keep the lights on and the kitchens humming we even make our own chairs we own and operate almost everything we need to ensure we continue to serve the highest quality food in the exciting comfortable environment that keeps our guests satisfied and coming back this type of business is called vertical integration and it helps us ensure theres never a holdup in the process and that we have the absolute best for our guests the moment they ask for it site map home about us our restaurants careers gift cards community relations restaurant locator news and events contact us site map get exclusive promotions list of locations terms of use privacy policy restaurants pappadeaux seafood kitchen pappasitos cantina pappas bros steakhouse pappas seafood house pappas barbq pappas burger yia yia marys mediterranean kitchen catering  deliv